Author: Heruur
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ROCKCHAIN : The distributed data intelligence (Start 1st nov 2017)
Body: Of course the project still on going even though we are very disappointed by the result. We know now with certitude that ICO market is helded by big investors/influencers and without them you can not succeed.  As planned and descibed in our crowdsale process we are going to refund all stakeholders in few days. We don't hope anymore to reach our soft cap fixed at 18.000 ETH to help us to accelerate our development.  Feel free to contribute and get free ROK tokens...  Enjoy it

Author: Heruur
Title: [ANN] [ICO] ROCKCHAIN : The distributed data intelligence (Start 1st nov 2017)
Body: Ethereum blockchain miners : your GPU is not dead.   You are mining on the Ethereum blockchain ? For that, you invested in expensive GPU computing power, and are now wondering what you will do once Casper, Ethereum's future "proof-of-stake" protocol, kicks in ?   What about earning ROK tokens by mining data script for Rockchain ?   Rockchain is a layer over Ethereum, allowing dApps to handle distributed data privacy. We are currently working on a new code version (due last quarter 2018) which in the future could potentially reward your mining for data script execution.   Unlike Ethereum’s current proof-of-work reward, Rockchain’s reward would be : . guaranteed . based on allocated calculation power . without any competition between miners   With Rockchain, give your GPU a second life.     Support our project and development efforts by joining our token sale on www.rockchain.org (ICO opens Nov 1st, 2017).
